# Bookstore Website

Welcome to our bookstore website repository! This project showcases a static web page for a bookstore website, offering various features and sections to explore.

## Features

- Services: Discover the range of services we offer, such as book recommendations, gift wrapping, and more.
- About Us: Learn about our bookstore's history, mission, and values.
- Featured Books: Explore a curated selection of featured books, handpicked by our team.
- New Arrivals: Stay up-to-date with the latest additions to our bookstore's collection.
- Reviews: Read reviews and testimonials from satisfied customers.
- Digital Books: Explore our collection of digital books, available for download or purchase.
- Our Blogs: Dive into our blog section, where we share book recommendations, author interviews, and more.

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Getting Started

To get a copy of this project up and running on your local machine, follow these steps:

1. Clone this repository to your local machine using `git clone`.

bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/bookstore-website.git
